name: DEENA BANDU FOUNDATION
briefDescription: Project Location = Ch.Pothapalli, West Godavari District, Andhra Pradesh, India.The number of beneficiaries = 200 old and disabled people.The frequency of distribution = daily.Number of villages served = 6 (Kodigudem, Moddulugudem, G Kothapalli, East Yadavalli, Ch.Pothapalli, Kommara)In the 2017 year = 62600 meals served.Since inception(2011) = 3,97,200.00 meals served .Our aim is = Thriving to serve 1000 people per day.
